Xorn are three-eyed, three-armed creatures from the Elemental Plane of Earth and Quasielemental+Plane+of+Mineral. Their primary diet is gems and precious stones. They cannot digest flesh, but will attack those who carry precious minerals if they refuse to give up a reasonable portion. On their home plane, xorn are generally peaceful and travel in small clans of mineral gatherers. Dao often hunt them for sport, or enslave them.
A variant species, the ash xorn, can be found in the Quasielemental+Plane+of+Ash. Another related race is the Xaren. There are four-armed xorn in the realm of Kali. 

